org.apache.beam.runners.flink.translation

Class FlinkStreamingPipelineTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.Pipeline.PipelineVisitor.Defaults
      • org.apache.beam.runners.flink.translation.FlinkPipelineTranslator
        • org.apache.beam.runners.flink.translation.FlinkStreamingPipelineTranslator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pipeline.PipelineVisitor

    public class FlinkStreamingPipelineTranslator
extends FlinkPipelineTranslator
    This is a FlinkPipelineTranslator for streaming jobs. Its role is to translate the user-provided PCollection-based job into a DataStream one.

        public Pipeline.PipelineVisitor.CompositeBehavior enterCompositeTransform(TransformTreeNode node)
        Description copied from interface: Pipeline.PipelineVisitor
        Called for each composite transform after all topological predecessors have been visited but before any of its component transforms.

        The return value controls whether or not child transforms are visited.
